    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702760/extras/330ee035bb9c167f583823daea973049.poster.avif?t=1770826645\" width=640 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702760/extras/330ee035bb9c167f583823daea973049.webm?t=1770826645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702760/extras/330ee035bb9c167f583823daea973049.mp4?t=1770826645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In next Life 是一个制作、生存及文明建造游戏。与其他玩家合作可以达到最佳游戏体验（也可以自己玩，但是会比较辛苦）。文明从石器时代开始，你及与族人努力一起研发及制作更多的工具及科技，像是生火、篮子、矛……以生存并且迈向更高层次的文明。时间过得很快，每次游玩等于体验一回的生老病死。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702760/extras/9668ec487d25dc01647bb224c0d86eef.poster.avif?t=1770826645\" width=640 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702760/extras/9668ec487d25dc01647bb224c0d86eef.webm?t=1770826645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702760/extras/9668ec487d25dc01647bb224c0d86eef.mp4?t=1770826645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>每一生的目标是为部落的文明提子女的未来贡献越多越好，你所留下的丰功伟业将成为后人迈向成功的基石。你制作的矛可能成为后代生死一战的重要武器。游戏内有超过百种可以搜集及制作的道具、工具、食物等。在抢先体验阶段我们打算再增加更多物品！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702760/extras/fb7c6db2d64e7078cbf017c0a861e887.poster.avif?t=1770826645\" width=640 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702760/extras/fb7c6db2d64e7078cbf017c0a861e887.webm?t=1770826645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702760/extras/fb7c6db2d64e7078cbf017c0a861e887.mp4?t=1770826645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>游戏一开始你通常是个宝宝，你会需要大人照顾你。随着时间你将长大成人，也会开始有自己的宝宝（其他玩家）。如果你能力够，可以活到终老。但是如果早死也没关系，可以投胎重来。有时候壮烈牺牲是保护族人必要手段！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702760/extras/58a7e44285ba9b53ea7335049baddec6.poster.avif?t=1770826645\" width=640 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702760/extras/58a7e44285ba9b53ea7335049baddec6.webm?t=1770826645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702760/extras/58a7e44285ba9b53ea7335049baddec6.mp4?t=1770826645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>你是一个热爱生命的灵魂，透过不断轮回学习并且体验这个世界。一开始你将体验人类发展初期。随着经验及知识的增加，将会发展更多人类文明。不管在哪个阶段，与其他玩家共同合作将是最有利的。你每一生的经验将会累计并且可以用于来世，让你成为一个更有贡献的族人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702760/extras/58a7e44285ba9b53ea7335049baddec6.poster.avif?t=1770826645\" width=640 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702760/extras/58a7e44285ba9b53ea7335049baddec6.webm?t=1770826645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702760/extras/58a7e44285ba9b53ea7335049baddec6.mp4?t=1770826645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
